<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-088-113 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 050 113</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  August 2 1991* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Grid 20 - 30% computer price cuts. (Grid Systems Corp.)andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Rohrbough, Linda.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Grid Systems Corp. (Prices and rates).andO;Topic:     Computer industryNotebook ComputersLaptop computersMicrocomputersPrice CuttingMarketing StrategyPromotion of Product.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>****GRID 20 - 30% COMPUTER PRICE CUTS 08/02/91 FREMONT, CALIFORNIA, U.S.A.,andO;1991 AUG 2 (NB) -- Grid Systems, responding to an industry trend, says it isreducing prices on all of its laptop, notebook and desktop computer systemsby 20 to 30 percent.andM;Bruce Walter, president of Grid, said, &quot;The Grid name has long representedrugged high-performance products backed by one of the industry's best directsales and support programs.andP;  These price reductions will continue to give ourcustomers those durable, reliable products at competitive prices.&quot;andM;Affected are Grid's computers, hard disk drives, random access memory (RAM)kits, central processing units (CPUs), coprocessors, and monitors, thecompany said.andP;  Some examples include the Grid 1450 laptop computer (an80386SX-based system), reduced from $5,295 (with 40 megabyte hard drive) to$3,995, the Grid 1720 notebook computer (an 80286-based system) reduced from$3,495 (with modem and 20MB hard drive) to $2,895 and the Grid 386isx-20desktop computer, reduced from $2,799 to $1,799.andP;  RAM kit prices weredecreased more than 25 percent, Grid said.andM;Grid said it has also revised its corporate discount structures as well.andM;Grid is a wholly owed subsidiary of Tandy Corporation headquartered in FortWorth, Texas.andP;  Grid's offices are located at 47211 Lakeview Blvd., Fremont,CA 94538.andP;  The company also has offices in the United Kingdom, Canada,Germany, Spain, Sweden, France, Belgium, and Denmark.andM;(Linda Rohrbough/19910802/Press Contact: Bob Goligoski, Grid, Tel:415/656-4700, Fax: 415/683-0902)</TEXT></DOC>